Yahoo Chairman Bostock Says Board Supports Chief Executive Bartz

-- B y   B r i a n   W o m a c k
-- 
2011-06-23T15:22:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/yahoo-chairman-bostock-says-board-supports-chief-executive-officer-bartz.html
Yahoo! Inc. Chairman Roy Bostock
said the company’s board is very supportive of Chief Executive
Officer  Carol Bartz .  Bostock, speaking to investors today at the company’s
annual shareholder meeting in  Santa Clara ,  California , said he
is confident the Web portal is headed in the right direction.
The Sunnyvale, California-based company has made progress in its
turnaround, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Womack in  San Francisco  at 
